      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. we've checked the logs and everything looks fine on the digital side, so it's not a system glitch. i'm really worried about the possibility of internal theft or maybe something more \"mysterious\" going on since items just seem to vanish from certain bins without any record. do you have any advice on detecting those kinds of \"untraceable\" losses?",
